Instructions: This tool is made for the game "!Ω Omega: My Dystopian Robot Girlfriend".
Warning - Spoilers! This tool lists a lot of information, so it contains spoilers. Please note!
To get started, select "Open File" -> "Read Save" and open your save file. Then select the save you want to check. This does not include automatic saves. If you want to save the save after modifying the data. Open "File" -> "Save Save, then start the game and import your modified save into the game.
Save Edits" -> "Save Overwrite Current Save" Prior to 0.90, your save files are in the following directory: [C:\Users\<YOUR USERNAME> (your user name)\AppData\LocalLow\IncontinentCell\My Dystopian Robot Girlfriend\Saves In versions 0.90 and later, your exported save files will be located in the location where you save the file.
